subject: "Sound Writing" by Kingsley Read

messageBody:
I have uploaded a Word file to the Resources folder in the Files
section. It is a scanned copy of a booklet entitled "Sound Writing"
and was the notes to accompany an exhibition staged at Reading
University, England in 1972.

I makes interesting reading and helps to put into perspective Read's
rationale behind the development of QS.

Moira
